Bad form.

87
00:03:31,130 --> 00:03:33,930
But, that’s still a point for Xi

88
00:03:33,930 --> 00:03:36,380
for largest volume of supporters.

89
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:39,099
But, then I also have to give Trump a point

90
00:03:39,099 --> 00:03:40,180
for his supporters,

91
