116
00:04:33,449 --> 00:04:34,720
This was the epic showdown

117
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,370
between the world’s two biggest economies.

118
00:04:37,370 --> 00:04:39,189
Superpower meets superpower.

119
00:04:39,189 --> 00:04:42,030
There’s got to be a winner!

120
00:04:42,030 --> 00:04:43,069
Hold on.

121
