125
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:52,830
and definitely not the McDonald’s

126
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:55,349
he’d threatened two years ago,

127
00:04:55,349 --> 00:04:57,849
Trump launches a missile strike against Syria,

128
00:04:57,849 --> 00:05:01,120
punishing Assad for his chemical attack on
civilians.

129
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,660
Boom!

130
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:05,860
Trump shows Xi that he is a man of action.

131
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:08,800
