134
00:05:13,689 --> 00:05:16,219
Plus it knocks the wind out of the claims

135
00:05:16,219 --> 00:05:18,250
Trump is a stooge of Russia.

136
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,350
Three points for Trump!

137
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:23,710
