Xi Jinping also agreed to,

216
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:38,430
“Lift China’s 13-year-long ban on U.S.
beef

217
00:08:38,430 --> 00:08:42,680
and buy more American grain and agricultural
products.”

218
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:44,690
And to further sweeten the pot,

219
