Xi and Trump agreed to a 100-day plan for
trade talks

220
00:08:48,190 --> 00:08:51,790
to discuss how to handle China’s trade surplus.

221
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,910
So that’s a point for President Trump,

222
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,079
because he got the Chinese

223
00:08:55,079 --> 00:08:58,190
to make big trade concessions.

224
00:08:58,190 --> 00:09:01,000
But it’s also a win for Xi Jinping.

225
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,019
In a masterful move

226
00:09:02,019 --> 00:09:03,730
that can only further demonstrate

227
00:09:03,730 --> 00:09:06,250
Xi Jinping’s knowledge of Taichi,

228
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:07,620
he absorbs the blow

229
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:10,639
and redirects it to his advantage.

230
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:13,200
See, by making these concessions,

231
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,300
Xi Jinping avoids the trade war

232
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:17,190
Trump has been threatening.

233
00:09:17,190 --> 00:09:21,550
And the kicker is, he does it for practically
nothing.

234
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,740
All these “concessions” to Trump

235
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:25,460
are actually things the Chinese government
was

236
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:26,529
