237
00:09:26,529 --> 00:09:28,910
with the Obama administration.

238
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:31,290
So another point for Xi, and...

239
00:09:31,290 --> 00:09:33,300
We’re tied again.

240
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,300
Really?

241
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:35,300
No.

242
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:36,829
This cannot end in a tie.

243
00:09:36,829 --> 00:09:39,450
There has to be something else we can look
at.

244
00:09:39,450 --> 00:09:40,709
What about their outfits?

245
00:09:40,709 --> 00:09:42,170
